        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Cultivated by mashing and fermenting toxic weeds found in lonely graveyards, *fearweed* is a greenish paste magically infused with psychic horror. The frightened condition from *fearweed* can't be removed while the poison lasts.",
        "level": 10,
